        {
            "title": "歐洲股市持平 投資者聚焦美俄會晤",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MnZ6G2X30EGEf7RT9b52zA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/736daaba4c51a6dd3dd101c5ac5b1442\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市表現平淡，投資者關注川普和普丁峰會，而丹麥珠寶商 潘多拉因盈利令人失望而下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克歐洲600指數收盤基本持平，此前一度上漲近0.5%，達到3月份以來的最高水平。該指數本周連續第二周上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">礦業和醫療健保板塊周五表現優異，而個人護理和房地產股則表現落後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">科技股下跌，應用材料公司業績展望疲軟，對艾司摩爾等晶片設備類股造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他方面，潘多拉重挫18%，此前其收入低於分析師平均預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國數據顯示7月零售銷售成長，但不及預期。市場關注焦點主要集中於唐納德·川普和弗拉基米爾·普丁稍後將在阿拉斯加舉行的會晤，投資者希望在結束烏克蘭戰爭方面看到進展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：川普與普丁阿拉斯加會談進入倒計時 這份交易攻略請查收</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞士隆奧投資管理公司宏觀主管Florian Ielpo表示，烏克蘭停火談判取得任何進展都將「對市場構成利好」，因為目前投資者並未為此做好倉位準備。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rPTRWU7UVOCcvkMf4P9u1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4a031e50f13ebe00fe4d944b63eef47a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Trade Steady With Focus on US-Russia Meeting</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika、Henry Ren.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6%E7%BE%8E%E4%BF%84%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4-162004892.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-16 01:40:50",
