        {
            "title": "芝加哥聯儲行長稱希望看到更多通膨壓力減緩的跡象",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Federal Reserve Bank of Chicago President Austan Goolsbee\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hVx.hza5f5Hs7SHFv9HAHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a501eabbb97cb17c93f680d89f335baf\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Federal Reserve Bank of Chicago President Austan Goolsbee</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 芝加哥聯儲行長Austan Goolsbee表示，他希望至少再看到一份通膨報告，以確保頑固的價格壓力沒有回升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「有些表現不一，」Goolsbee周五接受CNBC採訪時談到近期通膨數據時說。「我感覺我們至少還需要再看一份報告，來判斷我們是否仍處於黃金之路上。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Goolsbee重申了他本周早些時候的觀點，稱對周二公佈的7月CPI報告中服務業高通膨表示擔憂。但他也表示，不應對單月數據反應過度，包括周五公佈的數據顯示7月進口價格攀升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會官員今年以來一直維持利率不變，以觀察關稅等政策變化對美國經濟的影響。根據利率期貨數據顯示，投資者普遍押注聯儲會將在9月會議上重啟降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Goolsbee表示，他希望等待更多經濟數據出爐，並補充稱，「經濟中仍有很多強勁因素」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"芝加哥聯儲行長Austan Goolsbee攝影師：Rachel Mummey/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AZtQjPV7iGxvmz7Dob.5VA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3e544a4fc09cc2d0995efe55ca6a2da1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">芝加哥聯儲行長Austan Goolsbee攝影師：Rachel Mummey/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為我們確實需要弄清楚，這些價格上漲中哪些部分是我們覺得是暫時的而有所忽略，哪些是我們在回應的，」Goolsbee表示。「如果我們繼續收到類似(本月)四份報告中前兩份那樣的通膨報告，我會非常安心不確定性已經散去。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國7月零售銷售普遍攀升 前月數據有所上修 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Goolsbee Says He Wants to See More Positive Inflation Data</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%9D%E5%8A%A0%E5%93%A5%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E7%A8%B1%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E6%B8%9B%E7%B7%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%A1%E8%B1%A1-152921805.html",
